\title{the bottom value}
\p{Following [Scott](danascott), we introduce a special \em{bottom} value #{\bot} to our semantic domains.
##{\bot\ \text{represents}\ \begin{cases}\text{an undefined value;}\\\text{an error value;}\\\text{a \emph{non-terminating} computation.} \end{cases}}}
